kgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n矮仔</blockquote><br />\n3張野有冇辦法增高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左下世飲多兩包奶之外 諗唔到其他方法了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32373d78d5e7c0aec62666b6e44fd21261e5d55c","tid":258384,"uid":8678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:08:48.000Z","msg":"依種叫skinny fat 去gym 吧"},{"pid":"2e6d1e118f009e083f7d35b2c4432ac6795febec","tid":258384,"uid":17945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩畫條jer出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJJ樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d41fa85058b7a0d5c77a366dc8ce30d7a0deffc","tid":258384,"uid":87687,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全身瘦 但有肥肚 減唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/133553_ea707a067498aed03a5410a8df99634c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F133553_ea707a067498aed03a5410a8df99634c.jpg&h=098b0933&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇得減的。<br />\n<br />\n你呢種係肌肉量太少，個肚唔係肥，<br />\n係內臟，類似非洲飢荒兒童咁，<br />\n四肢得條骨，肚就脹，<br />\n唔通佢地要減肥？<br />\n<br />\n你呢種係低input 低output 既結果，<br />\n你係五十步，非洲兒童係一百步。<br />\n你離佢地不遠矣。<br />\n再減乜春都好，身體係永遠優先保養內臟先於肌肉，<br />\n個肚只會越減越突，好似d on9港女咁。<br />\n<br />\n解決辦法，<br />\n治本就係高input 高output,<br />\n因為內臟size 共本上冇辦法搞的<br />\n大量增加skeletal muscle,<br />\n做返大軀幹四肢，balance 返個size.<br />\n<br />\n治標就就係企好d坐好d ,<br />\n咪成日寒起個背，<br />\n望落冇咁樣衰，成個格好左會順眼好多。<br />\n<br />\n利申：有健身教練牌但唔係做呢行。"},{"pid":"6988fea91e5c773091ae6eb9a204f83741b4c32f","tid":258384,"uid":98,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我中學已經有肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e91e917f1a819d280378ac06c5fffbd074d29e3","tid":258384,"uid":94662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"見到隻胡說樹笑咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1057dd020882a603a72da38be883bd6f64507b8f","tid":258384,"uid":17448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全身瘦 但有肥肚 減唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/133553_ea707a067498aed03a5410a8df99634c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F133553_ea707a067498aed03a5410a8df99634c.jpg&h=098b0933&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇得減的。<br />\n<br />\n你呢種係肌肉量太少，個肚唔係肥，<br />\n係內臟，類似非洲飢荒兒童咁，<br />\n四肢得條骨，肚就脹，<br />\n唔通佢地要減肥？<br />\n<br />\n你呢種係低input 低output 既結果，<br />\n你係五十步，非洲兒童係一百步。<br />\n你離佢地不遠矣。<br />\n再減乜春都好，身體係永遠優先保養內臟先於肌肉，<br />\n個肚只會越減越突，好似d on9港女咁。<br />\n<br />\n解決辦法，<br />\n治本就係高input 高output,<br />\n因為內臟size 共本上冇辦法搞的<br />\n大量增加skeletal muscle,<br />\n做返大軀幹四肢，balance 返個size.<br />\n<br />\n治標就就係企好d坐好d ,<br />\n咪成日寒起個背，<br />\n望落冇咁樣衰，成個格好左會順眼好多。<br />\n<br />\n利申：有健身教練牌但唔係做呢行。</blockquote><br />\n我踩半個月單車就冇左個肚"},{"pid":"74a9852a8920c696fc6900a1c2842eb622b542eb","tid":258384,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26