eplyTime":"2017-05-26T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"樓豬啲畫好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85ba84efef271f8da9a7c4f6df697d8aa6b7d1e","tid":258384,"uid":22584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:43:47.000Z","msg":"認真回你 你係skinny fat"},{"pid":"f7a9d23aa8116e06e0b80f106fa3b012eccbd93b","tid":258384,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:22:14.000Z","msg":"D畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7aa312dab2ee70a3cf36fb04e2319658f50046","tid":258384,"uid":69939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打幾歲?<br />\n終於搵到一個同我一樣問題既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我168矮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  105磅超級排骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係個肚腩勁撚大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以點搞<br />\n利申:極度寒背但係企直左都有肚腩<br />\n返office工日日坐14個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nET外星人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8f70f4e2384e15091ef0ab7cc4916a5ab9041c","tid":258384,"uid":737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"瘦底但係全身脂肪係哂塊面度又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed936f3fe4ccbd34a56965bd99b5c3fd0dc804c","tid":258384,"uid":42971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我兩年前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同人講我邊度肥啊啲手腳咁幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但每次照鏡就會發覺自己比肥仔更加廢,呃唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肥仔起碼有力水<br />\n但自己又無力又中央肥胖,成日比人蝦<br />\n真係要食多啲野做多啲運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 173cm 之前43kg但係都有肚腩,而家57kg有腹肌,增緊磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n57kg都好輕 65就應該幾正 加油</blockquote><br />\n我目標都係65 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb246ea0e3b5fe67cf7e7d1957f0016b979ef1e3","tid":258384,"uid":77811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"媽...好亂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母！瘦底但全身脂肪......<br />\n屌你！老母瘦底但全身脂肪......<br />\n屌！你老母瘦底但全身脂肪......"},{"pid":"051465c278d3dd69178d28ffc258f3ad48d23c73","tid":258384,"uid":39852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>全身瘦 但有肥肚 減唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/133553_ea707a067498aed03a5410a8df99634c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F133553_ea707a067498aed03a5410a8df99634c.jpg&h=098b0933&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇得減的。<br />\n<br />\n你呢種係肌肉量太少，個肚唔係肥，<br />\n係內臟，類似非洲飢荒兒童咁，<br />\n四肢得條骨，肚就脹，<br />\n唔通佢地要減肥？<br />\n<br />\n你呢種係低input 低output 既結果，<br />\n你係五十步，非洲兒童係一百步。<br />\n你離佢地不遠矣。<br />\n再減乜春都好，身體係永遠優先保養內臟先於肌肉，<br />\n個肚只會越減越突，好似d on9港女咁。<br />\n<br />\n解決辦法，<br />\n治本就係高input 高output,<br />\n因為內臟size 共本上冇辦法搞的<br />\n大量增加skeletal muscle,<br />\n做返大軀幹四肢，balance 返個size.<br />\n<br />\n治標就就係企好d坐好d ,<br />\n咪成日寒起個背，<br />\n望落冇咁樣衰，成個格好左會順眼好多。<br />\n<br />\n利申：有健身教練牌但唔係做呢行。</blockquote><br />\n笑死<br />\n果然d健身教練都係垃圾<br />\n非洲兒童突果d係水<br />\n果個係病黎 叫kwashiorkor<br />\n學好d bio先做健身教練啦柒頭<br />\n基本常識都冇學人做教練</blockquote><br />\nBalance返個size唔係錯，但最重要嗰啲你冇講<br />\n一定要做cardio，游水跑步踩單車乜都好，每次做30分鐘above，咁先開始燒到脂<br />\n另外要有均衡飲食，多菜多纖維少肉少鹽少糖少油唔再講，唔好諗住亂咁節食，遲下食返正常份量反彈實肥到仆街<br />\nKeep住以上講嘅野去做返三個月啦<br />\n利申：9up"},{"pid":"208caac167cbda9200c6ebca5149a7a4a308630d","tid":258384,"uid":4607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"d comment笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}